","msg":"又想陷害警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a813e7eb6986a64f3f7afabbaacbafb595e819e","tid":260980,"uid":87182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T06:52:40.000Z","msg":"平時過路障都係同差人吹兩咀就過<br />\n<br />\n無啦啦屈你個fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又真係好無奈既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e8711ccc5c1a86ae7e39a7466b32fba37644462","tid":260980,"uid":9769,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T07:01:00.000Z","msg":"多年赤柱認識大量毒犯經驗，亦認識賣白粉的警察，事主講大話，警犬有2包白粉自己拿去賣左換錢，點會要黎做你！警察唔會咁on9帶白粉係身，仲要帶咁多，有咩事比親家督你個度起碼坐20年，蠢過閪都唔會咁做。<br />\n<br />\n你朋友單野，因為毒品係有判刑指引，純度1KG以上既話，最小14年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而因為香港唔使打把，所以毒品入罪門檻好低，唔使點樣證據，話你有就有！"},{"pid":"b541db1266a17c346327f679c2151c653cb4fbb8","tid":260980,"uid":8128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T08:02:10.000Z","msg":"暑假卜日"},{"pid":"24dda44591ab3f93c14d5f9b87c878b01cf0b76d","tid":260980,"uid":8128,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T08:03:28.000Z","msg":"又黎？ 如果係吹出黎樓主應該己經有法律責任。<br />\n似吹多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留名睇仆"},{"pid":"d246676cd6ef7f51289b7bbba7798f982a172ac4","tid":260980,"uid":24737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T08:08:37.000Z","msg":"留名跟進"},{"pid":"5e5b252b62273521d92537174fa08c936f85faad","tid":260980,"uid":71655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T08:10:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e5dc89c6127c75ff1ff86d7b8a9c47e40ce5274","tid":260980,"uid":48579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0