665c375a01970e4af0da63ea93ffd9fbb86d5c","tid":260980,"uid":40925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:32:25.000Z","msg":"之前褲袋冰毒咪又係老屈"},{"pid":"6dca7a4ba57f6d3f483f2795a62d11e6c35332af","tid":260980,"uid":98653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:34:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成個故仔都好假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n第一要證明個d 粉真係毒品<br />\n第二會驗下包粉有無你fd 指紋<br />\n之後先會上court<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：好似係</blockquote><br />\n唔需要指紋，一樣可以入到罪</blockquote><br />\n師兄此言差矣，如果包粉響自己架車到出現，而無自己既指紋，法律上絕對係有得打。控方要搵證據證明包粉係被告藏響車到，始終香港法律上暫時都未係大陸咁，未定罪前所有人都係清白，要定罪一個人就要控方搵證據證明被告人犯罪，所以如果包粉無指紋，未必入到罪。"},{"pid":"a776937902ed9beec69c91de49658db547126bf4","tid":260980,"uid":5123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:35:18.000Z","msg":"無間道 黎明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf32deab61d72fb7983ee613e047f9d1781934a","tid":260980,"uid":113776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:39:42.000Z","msg":"乜而家警察都要交數既咩？"},{"pid":"cec26921f340a026fb64f6453e3529b867489fd4","tid":260980,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:41:51.000Z","msg":"仲玩呢種野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黑警玩左幾十年都唔厭"},{"pid":"d1ca8e891d02621af3f13482f7c3690fc241c889","tid":260980,"uid":68135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:42:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b3b7f75c60ecf7af3a6e46cef791ccace32d441a","tid":260980,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:59:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩包粉咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁好心機買黎砌你朋友 唔好玩啦</blockquote><br />\n你知唔知班差佬拉完啲賣粉啲友<br />\n收返黎個啲粉轉頭就